                            <comment id="14427468" author="skaze" created="Sun, 21 May 2006 09:58:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Until core gets reporting sorted (ie. reportingManagement, dependencies for reports, etc) we define the checkstyle, clover-2.0 and pmd plugins as &amp;lt;build&amp;gt; plugins and specify their dependencies in the nornmal plugin way. Fortunately they dont have default goals bound to the lifecycle so don&apos;t do any harm in the normal biuld but when the report or check mojos are invoked either by site or via explicit invocation the plugin configuration seems to inherit the &amp;lt;build&amp;gt; defined configuration, including its dependencies.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
