                            <comment id="16429402" author="gboue" created="Sat, 7 Apr 2018 15:01:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is fixed since the Site plugin 3.0 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSITE-444&quot; title=&quot;reporting section should allow additional dependencies in plugins as well&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MSITE-444&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MSITE-444&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). You can declare dependencies in &lt;tt&gt;pluginManagement&lt;/tt&gt; section and it will be inherited by report plugins like checkstyle.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
